{{otheruses4|the mosque in the [[City of Brass]]|the mosque [[Krak al-Niraan]]|Mosque of Kossuth (Krak al-Niraan)}}
The '''Mosque of [[Kossuth]]''' was a temple located in the [[City of Brass]] in [[1367 DR]].{{AQ-time}}

This mosque was found in [[Furnace (district)|the Furnace ward]] of the city.
